steps.instruction:
Fill out the 'Create New Service Ticket' form with these values:
1. In the 'Title' field, enter: {{title}}
2. In the 'Description' textarea, enter: {{description}}
3. Select '{{category}}' from the 'Category' dropdown
4. Select '{{priority}}' from the 'Priority' dropdown
5. In the 'Requester' field, enter: {{requester}}
Leave the Due Date field as is - do not modify it.
Do NOT click the Create Ticket button yet.

In the 'Allocate Inventory Item' modal:
1. In the 'Employee Name' field, enter: {{employee_name}}
2. In the 'Quantity to Allocate' field, enter: {{quantity}}
3. In the 'Reason/Notes' textarea, enter: {{notes}}
